**Do not select Panasonic/PHCbi MDF-DU702VH-PA as a primary routine vaccine refrigerator.** It is an ultra-low-temperature freezer, not a 2°C–8°C refrigerator. It may be appropriate only for ultra-cold vaccine or biologic storage requiring approximately -90°C to -60°C or -80°C conditions.

