| 10-year kWh, 8 units | 90,228 kWh | 130,232 kWh | 262,800 kWh |
| 10-year energy cost | 90,228 × R | 130,232 × R | 262,800 × R |
| Benchmark monitoring | ~$20,528 | ~$20,528 or Smart-Vue quote | ~$20,528 or ULT monitoring quote |

At **R = $0.10/kWh**, energy cost over 10 years would be approximately:

| Product | 10-year energy cost, 8 units |
|---|---:|
| Helmer | $9,023 |
| Thermo | $13,023 |
| Panasonic ULT | $26,280 |

